</P>
<P>
The Frenchman won two tiles early in the year but failed to get past the fourth
round at either the French Open or Wimbledon. Has blown hot and cold in the
buildup to Flushing Meadows losing early in Washington before reaching the semi-
finals at the Montreal Masters where he lost a close one to Andy Murray. Tsonga
has yet to make it past the third round at the US Open but he was the junior
champion in New York in 2003 and loves the big occasion.
</P>
<P>
