</P>
<P>
Grand Slam titles: 0
</P>
<P>
Career Tour Titles 2
</P>
<P>
Best US Open result: Fourth round 2005
</P>
<P>
Stepped up a level at the start of the year with a run to the Australian Open
semi-finals where he took Nadal all the way before losing in five sets. Lost in
the fourth round at the French Open and Wimbledon and struggled since then until
the Montreal Masters where he was unlucky to lose to Roddick in a top quality
third round tie. Could be running into form at the right time for New York
</P>
